## Medical Disclaimer

This software is designed for clinical decision support purposes only. It is NOT intended to:

- Replace professional medical judgment
- Provide definitive medical diagnoses
- Substitute for consultation with qualified healthcare professionals
- Be used as the sole basis for clinical decisions

All AI-generated suggestions must be reviewed and verified by qualified healthcare professionals before implementation in patient care. The developers and contributors assume no liability for any clinical decisions made based on this software.

Use of this software in clinical settings should comply with all applicable local, national, and international healthcare regulations, including but not limited to HIPAA, GDPR, and local medical device regulations.
